de.schenk.jrtrace.annotations

Annotation Type XInvokeReturn


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface XInvokeReturn
    The first parameter of the injected method may be annotated with XInvokeReturn if and only if the XMethod.location() is set to . In this case the value of the return value of the previously invoked method will be available in the first paramter.
    Author:
    Christian Schenk
